Flights could be subject to short-notice cancellations. Some airlines, including British Airways have already stopped operating flights out of Malaysia and more could follow in the coming days. Further controls on travel within Malaysia may be imposed at short notice. Visitors to Malaysia should plan accordingly, taking account of the fast moving situation and your individual circumstances.
